    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable for daily commutes and still looks great parked in the driveway. It's been well-loved and taken care of, so you can just hop in and go! I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
